config SYS16_TEXTCON
	bool "System16 GoRV32 hardware text console"
	depends on VT && OF
	default n
	help
	  Console driver for the System16 GoRV32 FPGA hardware text mode: an
	  80x25 character-cell grid rendered from an on-chip 8x16 font ROM,
	  reached through the AXI slave window (cells at 0xE8000000, registers
	  at 0xE8800000). Cells are 16 bit (code + VGA-style attribute), so
	  output and scrolling move a couple of bytes per character instead of
	  a graphical framebuffer's pixels. Pairs with the USB-HID keyboard
	  for a full text console without a framebuffer.
